    DefaultConsumerAgentMessageScheme

    public abstract class ConsumerAgentMessageScheme
extends MessageScheme
    Class representing an abstraction of message schemes originating from consumer agents. This class is (currently) used only to structure the respective MessageSchemes and doesn't offer any additional functionality.
